      <title>科威特指责伊朗试图渗透其领土</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/12/world/middleeast/kuwait-iran-bubiyan-island.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科威特内政部表示，一群武装伊朗人于5月1日乘坐租来的渔船抵达波斯湾布比扬岛，并与科威特士兵交火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/12/world/middleeast/kuwait-iran-bubiyan-island.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 19:49:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和习近平因伊朗战争而参加中国峰会</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/12/us/politics/trump-xi-summit.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗战争给这两个超级大国蒙上了不确定性的阴影，使人们最初对两国能够开始解决破坏两国关系的更大问题的希望变得渺茫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/12/us/politics/trump-xi-summit.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 19:30:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Mamdani 和 Hochul 如何解决纽约市的预算危机</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/12/nyregion/mamdani-budget-nyc.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[州长凯西·霍楚尔 (Kathy Hochul) 提供的慷慨国家资源以及对豪华第二套住房征收的新税将帮助市长佐兰·马姆达尼 (Zohran Mamdani) 平衡 1,250 亿美元的预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/12/nyregion/mamdani-budget-nyc.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 19:28:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马蒂·马卡里 (Marty Makary)，特朗普的 FDA专员在数周压力后辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/12/us/politics/trump-fires-fda-commissioner-makary.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在马卡里博士私下表示反对政府批准调味电子烟的决定后，该机构的最高食品官员将接替这一职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/12/us/politics/trump-fires-fda-commissioner-makary.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 18:56:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>多囊卵巢综合征已更名为 P.M.O.S.医生希望它能改善数百万人的护理。</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/12/well/live/pcos-pmos-name-change-treatment-health.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这种疾病已被重新命名为多内分泌代谢性卵巢综合征（P.M.O.S.），以更好地反映其广泛的健康影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/12/well/live/pcos-pmos-name-change-treatment-health.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 18:56:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>官员称，倒影池的修复工作似乎参差不齐且落后于计划</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/12/us/politics/lincoln-memorial-pool-repairs.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标志性国家广场盆地的工程似乎落后于计划。特朗普总统最初表示他已经选择了承包商，然后又说他不知道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/12/us/politics/lincoln-memorial-pool-repairs.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 18:26:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于赫格斯挪用资金，五角大楼将伊朗战争成本定为 290 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/12/us/politics/iran-war-cost-hegseth-congress.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国防部最高预算官员的估计比两周前增加了 40 亿美元。国务卿皮特·赫格斯拒绝透露政府何时会为伊朗冲突请求额外资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/12/us/politics/iran-war-cost-hegseth-congress.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 18:02:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
